Language: <F P=105> Hebrew </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The police have decided to confiscate all weapons 
possessed by Kakh activists and others associated with them in 
Qiryat Arba'. Our correspondent Aviv Bushinsky reports that 
the hunt for four Kakh fugitives continues. The police broke 
into several Kakh-owned homes in Qiryat Arba' yesterday, but 
their inhabitants were not there. 

